quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  3,1,"Alif, Laam, Miim."
  3,2,"Alla: rewetee…óo woo alaa si wanaa KaŇčko. Ko o wuur…óo, √Īii…ďu…óo."
  3,3,"O Jippinirii deftere nden dow maa…óa e goonga, goonginnde ko adii nde o Jippini Tawreeta e Linnjiila."
  3,4,"Ko adii, fii fewnugol yim…ďe …ďen, o Jippini AlQur'aana. Pellet yeddu…ďe aayeeje Alla …óen, hino woodani …ďe le…ďte sa…ótu…óe. Alla ko foolu…óo, Joom njo…ďtiigu."
  3,5,"Pellet, Alla, huunde suu…óotaako mo ka leydi wanaa ka kammu."
  3,6,"Ko kaŇčko woni mba'dinoowo on ka renngaaji no o muuyiri. Rewetee…óo woo alaa si wanaa kaŇčko, foolu…óo, √Īee√Īu…óo."
  3,7,"Ko KaŇčko Woni Jippin…óo Deftere nden e maa…óa, no e mayre aayeeje …ďaŇčngu…óe; ko kanje woni neene deftere nden, e go…ó…óe goo nanndu…óe. Ammaa …ďen …ďe oo√Īaare woni e nder …ďer…óe mun, hi…ďe jokka ko nanndi kon e majje …óa…ď…ďugol fitina e …óa…ďugol firtugol …óe. Anndataa firo majje si wanaa Alla. Tutii…ďe …ďen e ganndal no wi'a: "Men gom…óinii nde, kala mun ko immorde ka Joomi amen". Waajitotaako si wanaa joomiraa…ďe haqqillaaji …ďen."
  3,8,"joomi amen, wata oo√Īu …ďer…óe amen …óen …ďaawo nde fewnu-…óaa men, ye…óu men yurmeende immorde ka maa…óa.Pellet ko aan woni dokko."
  3,9,"Joomi amen, pellet ko a moo…ďoyoowo yim…ďe …ďen √Īalnde nde sikke alaa he mun pellet Alla luutintaa fodoore nden."